{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji17.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致彭德怀电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电！!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年11月17日）德怀同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）送大批干部回后方保存甚为必要，后方经济虽困难，但可组织干部团，实行屯田政策及分散到后方部队中担任副职，一部分则进军事学校或党校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）胡服同志现到何处，是否还在总部，过封锁线有困难否，望告。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七日[1]这是毛泽东给中共北方局书记、八路军副总司令彭德怀的电报。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1942,"month":11,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":212,"page_end":212},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}